title: Kimi to dake wa Koi ni Ochinai
original_name: キミとだけは恋に堕ちない
sinopse:
Subaru has always lived her life behind the back of her two perfect, overprotective, big brothers. Everything starts to change when she meets Yoshida Arata, a strange, funny, troublemaker guy, different from everyone she knows.

(Source: SNShoujo)
